data.meta_description: Local listings for 'The Kelly Clarkson Show.' Find out what time and on what channel it airs in your local market..
data.text: "The Kelly Clarkson Show" airs weekdays. Find out where and when the show airs in the local listings below. In Canada? Click here. In Australia, The Kelly Clarkson Show airs weekdays at 9:00am on 7Bravo and 7plus.
